{
"#tip"
:
[
{
"cn"
:
"ps 显示的是当前通过 worker 运行的任务进程\n与 `x agent job ls` 不同：ps 看进程，ls 看任务目录\n"
,
"en"
:
"ps shows currently running worker processes\nUnlike `x agent job ls`: ps shows processes, ls shows job directories\n"
}
]
,
"#synopsis"
:
[
"x agent ps"
]
,
"#tldr"
:
[
{
"cmd"
:
"x agent ps"
,
"cn"
:
"示例: 查看运行中的任务进程"
,
"en"
:
"Example: View running job processes"
}
]
}

